  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ gas 6</p><p>Chop the <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into bite-sized pieces and add to a baking tray</p><p>Drizzle with <strong>vegetable oil</strong>,<strong> </strong>add the <strong>ground</strong> <strong>turmeric </strong>with a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 20-25 min or until crisp and cooked through – these are your <strong>turmeric roast potatoes</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1631622224400-x200.jpg",
