            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely dice 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>red onion</strong></p><p>Slice the <strong>remaining onion</strong> as finely as you can</p><p>Dice the <strong>tomatoes</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>green chilli<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
