            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced onion</strong> with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until starting to soften</p><p>While the onion softens, peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Once the onion has softened, add the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>with the<strong> ground cumin</strong>,<strong> ground coriander</strong> and <strong>half </strong>the <strong>chopped chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Cook for 1-2 min further or until fragrant</p>",
